    "description": "Wabash National India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Supply Chain Manager at our Surat location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Wabash National India:\nWabash National India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Coordinate with customer service teams to resolve delivery issues\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Ensure proper handling, packaging, and labeling of goods\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in Customs Clearance\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in Cold Chain Logistics\n• Proficiency in WMS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Surat, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Wabash National India!",
